OL,6,FA PSNI civilian detention officer has
OL,7,Fbeen sacked after getting a suspended
OL,8,Fprison sentence for assaulting a
OL,9,Fdetainee in a custody suite.
OL,11,FThe victim was drunk at the time and
OL,12,Fhad already been restrained before he
OL,13,Fwas attacked.
OL,15,FThe situation was described as being
OL,16,F"volatile" after the man threatened
OL,17,Fthe officer and another colleague.
