OL,12,Fsuspicion of breaching his bail
OL,13,Fconditions and assaulting police.
OL,14,FPolice Ombudsman Mrs Marie Anderson
OL,15,Fsaid: "This was a volatile situation,
OL,16,Fbut it was also a serious and
OL,17,Funwarranted assault on a man who was
OL,18,Fintoxicated.
