OL,19,Fforearm to "slam" him against a wall.
OL,20,FThe other CDO, who was dealing with
OL,21,Fthe man's property, then rushed to
OL,22,Fassist and the man was taken to the
OL,23,Fground. The assault happened as the
OL,24,FCDOs held on to his arms and head and
OL,25,Ftried to apply handcuffs.JAn audible
OL,26,Fpop could be heard on the CCTV footage
