OL,8,FDuffield said: "We expect the highest
OL,9,Fstandards of professionalism and
OL,10,Fintegrity from all of our police
OL,11,Fofficers and police staff and where
OL,12,Fconduct falls short of these high
OL,13,Fstandards, it is right that officers
OL,14,For designated staff should face an
OL,15,Fimpartial, thorough enquiry by the
OL,16,FPolice Ombudsman's office.J"The Police
OL,17,FService accepted the findings of the
